        Selling in Sherwood 2026
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Sherwood is the inner south-west corridor's family heartland. Its buyer pool draws from Chelmer and Graceville overflow, and its own strong character home identity. Here is what sellers need to know.
      </p>
    </div>
